com.sun.tools.visualvm.core.datasource

Class DataSourceProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.tools.visualvm.core.datasource.DataSourceProvider
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DataSourceContainer, DataSourceRepository

    public class DataSourceProvider
extends Object
    Default implementation of DataSourceProvider. DataSourceProviders can benefit from extending this class which implements managing created DataSource instances and firing the events to listeners.
    Author:
    Jiri Sedlacek
